qas.question: In the semi-additive process, what do the areas exposed by the mask become at the end?
What metal is used to plate the unmasked parts of the board in the semi-additive method?

What weight of plating is possible with copper?

plausible_answers.text: the board in the unmasked areas; copper may be plated to any desired weight
